div.p: The text presented here has been brought up to date on the basis of the study of the original and infrared pictures (for the Florence part). The basis of the text is Zuckerman's edition but we have introduced corrections and changes (sometimes returning to Vitelli's text). Only in cases where the new readings affect the content of the text, have we indicated the source. There are a number of cases where the placing of brackets has been changed, letters dotted or undotted and diacritical marks have been checked and reintroduced; these changes have not been signaled individually in the apparatus. All pages (I, II, III, IV, V, VI, VII, VIII, IX, X, XI, XII, XIII, XIV, XV, XVI, XVII and XVIII) have now been brought up to date.
